on with ½ tsp salt and ground black pepper and drizzle with marinade. Secure Varoma lid and cook <b>20 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b>. Set covered Varoma aside on a plate to keep warm."},{"content":"Add cream to mixing bowl, insert measuring cup and blend <b>2 min\/speed 5<b>-<b>10, increasing speed gradually from speed 5 to speed 10.<b> Serve soup for starter (see Tips), then salmon fillets and broccoli for main course."}],"hintsAndTricks":["If the celery stalks have leaves, place a few leaves on top of salmon fillets before steaming to add extra flavour.<br>- For a milder flavour, omit marinade in <b>step 3.<b><br>- After serving the soup, set mixing bowl and covered Varoma back in position so the main course stays warm."],"basicInfo":["easy","25m","50m","4 portions"]}